tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review:
I was suffering from dental problems for a long time and neglected and delayed any treatment because of fear. 
All my teeth started decaying and it came to a point where I had to get them fixed. 
A friend of mine recommended me to see Dr. Manish Kachhara. 
All my initial apprehension disappeared in the first appointment when he understood my problems, analysed them and offered me a couple of solutions, explaining all the steps and pros and cons of each. 
It was brilliantly systematic. 
We decided to go for full mouth implant supported fixed teeth. 
Every procedure right from treatment planning to surgery to temporary teeth to final fixed teeth was performed perfectly keeping in mind my fear, apprehension and comfort. 

I thought I would have to be without teeth for a couple of months as is standard with implant procedures but was so happy that Dr.Manish gave me fixed temporary teeth on the day of surgery. 
Imagine going in without teeth and coming out of the clinic with fixed teeth.... Yes. MAGIC. 

The clinic is equipped with state of the art machines including advanced imaging services like OPG and Lasers. 

The final outcome is way beyond my expectations and I cannot stop smiling. 

I would like to thank Dr. Manish and his team for the wonderful job on my teeth. 
Very highly recommended.
